{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/extras/g.gif?t=1738705075\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i><u>STORY &amp; ABOUT THE GAME:</u></i><br>The game &quot;Sleep Terror&quot; is a horror game created by a single developer. The title focuses on a variety of levels and different gameplay patterns. Each level offers something different - from traversing tight labyrinths in the garden where the Wendigo lurks to traversing the levels of the creepypasta &quot;Backrooms&quot;.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/extras/gif1.gif?t=1738705075\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wander through the nooks and crannies of your house in the dark, find fuses to turn on the electricity, and the fun begins moments after you go to bed. If you even make it home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/extras/HighresScreenshot00001.png?t=1738705075\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i><u>EXPLORE DREAM:</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wander through your nightmares, some of them contain AI opponents who will not have friendly intentions towards you, some of them involve exploring places hoping that you won't meet anyone or anything or nothing will jump out at you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/extras/gh.gif?t=1738705075\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i><u>BODYCAM/VHS:</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game has a BODYCAM VHS filter that you can turn on with one click without even going to the settings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/extras/gif_3.gif?t=1738705075\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i><u>TOOLS:</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use every thing that a given level offers you - flashlights, candles, maps or night vision goggles in the forest will certainly come in handy and help you escape!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <strong><i>FEATURES:</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25fd Game created by 1 developer </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25fdRealistic BodyCam/VHS effect (can be turned on/off with one key) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25fdAnimated 3D jumpscares</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u25fdRealistic environment </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25fd Varied maps </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25fdPuzzle </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25fdAdditional content after completing the game in the form of mini-games </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25fd Easter Eggs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Add the game to your wishlist so you don't miss the release and support my work!</u>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/extras/wish.gif?t=1738705075\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738705075","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/page.bg.jpg?t=1738705075","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/0827ea63525d99672c542d6ff94a7d9ca58e0f6b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738705075","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2879710/0827ea63525d99672c542d6ff94a7d9ca58e0f6b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738705075","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Sta